gw.plugin.reinsurance

Interface IReinsurancePlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin, java.rmi.Remote

    public interface IReinsurancePlugin
extends com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin
    The interface to a configurable module for reinsurance. NOTE: this interface should not have reference to any types that are specific to our implementation like: RIRisk, RIProgram, RIAttachment...
